data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged.  2024 PRICE ADJUSTMENT.  FIND OUT MORE!    Welcome to paradise in South Gulf Cove, Port Charlotte's sought-after waterfront community. This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a spacious and inviting layout spanning 2256 square feet. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the charm and comfort of this spacious gem. THE BEST PART!!! NEW, NEW, NEW. The owners had a new roof installed in June 2022. Then came the floors in June 2023: New Vinyl Flooring was installed in the master bedroom.  New laminate (water-resistant ) flooring was installed in the living room, family room, dining room, hallway and bedrooms 1 and 2. Then came the bathrooms and laundry room where porcelain tile was added. Kitchen cabinets were resurfaced and as a final touch, painting the walls was completed and added was new 5" base board. The heart of the home boasts a generous kitchen featuring an island with a second sink for the cook of the family.  The kitchen overlooks the cozy family room, perfect for gatherings and entertainment. The well-appointed kitchen offers ample counter space and storage, making meal preparation a breeze. The dining room and living room combination provides a versatile space for formal dinners or relaxed lounging. One of the highlights of this property is the beautiful fenced-in backyard, a true oasis. Enjoy the Florida sunshine and outdoor living to the fullest with an above-ground pool, creating a private retreat for cooling off during those warm summer days.  Wait what about all of those pool toys?  Also included in the back yard is the 10x 14 shed.  Just what you needed to complete the package.  Check it out today.  ALL OFFERS CONSIDERED. Please note:  Buyer is to pay title.
